{
  "subject": "Your agent still doesn't know anything about you.",
  "preheader": "Three days in, zero decisions logged. Here's the fastest way to fix that.",
  "text": "Hi,\n\nEvery session your agent starts cold until Marrow has enough decisions to recognize your patterns.\n\nFastest path if you're using Claude Code:\n\n`npx @getmarrow/mcp setup --api-key {{api_key}}`\n\nThat gets Marrow into the loop immediately.\n\nIf you're wiring it directly into Node.js instead:\n\n```ts\nimport MarrowClient from '@getmarrow/sdk'\n\nconst marrow = new MarrowClient('{{api_key}}')\nawait marrow.think({ action: 'first test', type: 'general' })\nawait marrow.commit({ success: true, outcome: 'done' })\n```\n\nEither version is enough to start building history.\n\nBuu, founder",
  "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n    <title>Your agent still doesn't know anything about you.</title>\n  </head>\n  <body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#0a0a0a;color:#e5e7eb;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;mso-hide:all;visibility:hidden;\">Three days in, zero decisions logged. Here's the fastest way to fix that.</div>\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#0a0a0a;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 12px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#0f1115;border:1px solid #1f2937;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td style=\"height:4px;background:#6f7cff;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td style=\"padding:32px 32px 14px 32px;\">\n                <div style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,'Liberation Mono','Courier New',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9aa4ff;\">MARROW</div>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td style=\"padding:0 32px 36px 32px;color:#e5e7eb;\">\n                <div style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;color:#9ca3af;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 14px 0;\">Day 3 nudge</div>\n                <h1 style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:32px;line-height:1.15;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;\">Your agent still doesn't know anything about you.</h1>\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;color:#9ca3af;\">Three days in is the right moment to fix this, before cold starts become your default.</p>\n\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#d1d5db;\">Every session your agent starts cold until Marrow has enough decisions to recognize your patterns.</p>\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;color:#9aa4ff;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">Fastest path in Claude Code</p>\n                <div style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0;padding:16px 18px;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1f2937;border-radius:12px;color:#f9fafb;font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,'Liberation Mono','Courier New',monospace;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;word-break:break-word;\">npx @getmarrow/mcp setup --api-key {{api_key}}</div>\n\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#d1d5db;\">If you're wiring it directly into Node.js instead:</p>\n                <div style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0;padding:16px 18px;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1f2937;border-radius:12px;color:#f9fafb;font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,'Liberation Mono','Courier New',monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;white-space:pre-wrap;\">import MarrowClient from '@getmarrow/sdk'\n\nconst marrow = new MarrowClient('{{api_key}}')\nawait marrow.think({ action: 'first test', type: 'general' })\nawait marrow.commit({ success: true, outcome: 'done' })</div>\n\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 22px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#d1d5db;\">Either version is enough to start building history.</p>\n\n                <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#ffffff;\">Buu, founder</p>\n\n                <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-top:1px solid #1f2937;padding-top:18px;\">\n                  <tr>\n                    <td style=\"padding-top:18px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#9ca3af;\">\n                      <a href=\"{{unsubscribe_url}}\" style=\"color:#9aa4ff;text-decoration:none;\">Unsubscribe</a><br />\n                      Marrow · made by Buu and a small team.\n                    </td>\n                  </tr>\n                </table>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>"
}